title: Kitchen Scale Sencor SKS 31GR
description:
4 High precision strain gauge sensors
Tare function to reset during weighing
Acrylic uniform surface for easy and hygienic maintenance
Contrast backlight for easy readability
Capacity 11lbs (division 0.03oz)
Automatic shut off when idle 60s
Overload & low battery indication
Included accessories: Alkaline 3x1.5V AAA zinc and manganese dioxide battery
http://www.sencor.us/home-appliances/kitchen-scales
